    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The interior is spotless, the paint is glowing, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, 'new car' feel without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
