    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, this chassis has been fastidiously maintained with a proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection, while the undercarriage remains concours-clean. A purist\u2019s specification with zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
